+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                             MINDBOLT
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

	Level: 1
	Cost: 45
	Type: Aggressive
	Damage: Based on Level
	Text: mindbolt <target>

        This is the first attack power learned by a psionicist. By
        the use of his mind, a psionicist can fire a bolt of force
        at a target.

